		<td width="550" align="left" valign="top" style="font-family:'Century Gothic',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:18px;line-height:22px;color:#ea007a"><strong>TELL YOUR FRIENDS - LEADERS NEEDED!</strong></td>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		</tr>
		
		<tr>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		<td width="550" align="center" valign="top"><img src="http://www.ncsthechallenge.org/images/staffing/Images/ncstc_hr_290914.jpg" width="550" height="22" border="0" style="display:block"></td>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		</tr>
		
		<tr>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		<td width="550" align="left" valign="top" style="font-family:'Century Gothic',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:15px;line-height:20px;color:#222222">
		
			<table width="550" align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0"><tbody><tr>
			
			<td align="left" valign="top"><img src="http://www.ncsthechallenge.org/images/photos/ncstc_staff-sideimg-skill2_211014.jpg" alt="" width="250" height="300" border="0"></td>
			
			<td align="left" valign="top"><p>You're probably sick about us shouting about this now, but one more time... <strong>Applications for summer 2016 are open now!</strong></p>


			<p>We especially need energetic, enthusiastic and encouraging people to join our seasonal workforce as Programme Leaders and Assistant Programme Leaders. If you think your friend or colleague has the confidence and skills to manage and lead a group of 60+ young people and 15+ staff through our intensive residential programme, <a href="http://www.ncsthechallenge.org/jobs/
" target="_blank">direct them to our website!</a></p></td>
			
