			<td align="left" valign="top"><p><strong>Free workshops on inclusion, SEND and creating opportunities in music & drama:</strong><br>
			<a href="http://www.musiceducationexpo.co.uk/" target="_blank">Music Education Expo</a> and Musical Theatre & Drama Education Show join forces this year to offer music & drama teachers over 44 hours of free CPD. Get stuck into a range of all-singing, all-dancing practical workshops, lively panel debates and key seminars presenting new educational trends and approaches, focusing on SEND and inclusion.</p>

<p><strong>When?</strong> 25 - 26 February 2016</p>
<p><strong>Where?</strong> Olympia London</p>

<p><a href="http://www.musiceducationexpo.co.uk/" target="_blank">View the full conference programme here.</a><br>
